snippet.title: Legendarium Online - GAMEPLAY TRAILER - Pre-Alpha v.0.1.0
snippet.description:
Legendarium Online - new 3D sandbox MMORPG with huge open world. Non-target system, no levels, no classes. Hundreds of combination for your unique play style. 
Currently is in early development process.
